<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
{{> head}}
<style>
  .pillar-card { transition: all 0.2s; }
  .pillar-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(117,71,255,0.12); }
</style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen text-gray-900">

<header class="bg-black text-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-6">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
      <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-purple-500 animate-pulse"></div>
      <span class="font-bold text-purple-400 text-sm tracking-wider">{{brand.name}} · CURSO SELLIVER v4</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-3">Curso Personalizado · {{selliver.name}}</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mt-1">Live de {{live.date}} · {{hero.nome_padrao}} · {{live.live_duration_min}} minutos</p>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">

  <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">4 Pilares · 75-90 min · 2 sessões</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">Cada pilar tem drills + quiz. A Prova Final (Pilar 4) libera você pro ar.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-sm">
      <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-lg text-center"><strong class="text-purple-600 block text-lg">P1</strong><span class="text-xs text-gray-600">Produto</span></div>
      <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-lg text-center"><strong class="text-purple-600 block text-lg">P2</strong><span class="text-xs text-gray-600">Cliente</span></div>
      <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-lg text-center"><strong class="text-purple-600 block text-lg">P3</strong><span class="text-xs text-gray-600">Concorrência</span></div>
      <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-lg text-center"><strong class="text-purple-600 block text-lg">P4</strong><span class="text-xs text-gray-600">Estado + Live</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero SKU Card -->
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-900 to-black text-white rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8">
    <div class="text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold tracking-wider mb-1">PRODUTO HERO</div>
    <div class="text-xs text-purple-400 mb-2">{{categoryLabel hero.category}}</div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1">{{hero.nome_padrao}}</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-3">{{hero.nome_oficial}}</p>
    <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm">
      <span class="text-gray-400 line-through">R$ {{hero.price_full}}</span>
      <span class="text-green-300 font-black text-xl">R$ {{hero.price_live}}</span>
      <span class="text-purple-300">· {{live.master_coupon}}</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">📚 Os 4 Pilares</h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">Sessão 1 (45min): Pilares 1 + 2 · Sessão 2 (45min): Pilares 3 + 4.</p>

  <div class="space-y-3">

    <div class="text-xs text-purple-600 font-bold tracking-wider mt-4">SESSÃO 1 · 45 min</div>

    <a href="01-produto.html" class="pillar-card block bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-100">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">PILAR 1 · 20 min</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">🏷️ Produto</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Descrição 60s · 3 diferenciais em ordem de impacto · 3 defeitos com resposta · compliance · ângulo da live.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-purple-600 mt-2">Drill: descrever o produto sem ler em 60s · Quiz P1 (5 perguntas)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-purple-600 text-xl">→</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="02-cliente.html" class="pillar-card block bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-100">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">PILAR 2 · 20 min</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">👤 Cliente</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Persona narrada (não demografia) · 5 Whys · JTBD · Belief Charts (5 instalar / 5 derrubar).</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-purple-600 mt-2">Drill: refrasear 5 frases marketeiras ≤15s · Quiz P2 (4 perguntas)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-purple-600 text-xl">→</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <div class="text-xs text-purple-600 font-bold tracking-wider mt-6">SESSÃO 2 · 45 min</div>

    <a href="03-concorrencia.html" class="pillar-card block bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-100">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">PILAR 3 · 15 min</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">⚔️ Concorrência</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Tabela comparativa · diferencial inegociável · Pix + 7 dias garantia (frase decorada).</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-purple-600 mt-2">Drill: responder comparação de preço em ≤30s · Quiz P3 (3 perguntas)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-purple-600 text-xl">→</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="04-estado-live.html" class="pillar-card block bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-purple-50 rounded-xl p-5 border-2 border-red-300">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-red-600 font-bold mb-1">PILAR 4 · 30 min · 🔴 PROVA FINAL</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">🎬 Estado + Execução Live</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Pré-suasão 0-7min · 5 hooks · ciclo completo · gift triggers · carrinho-opens · plano B.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-red-600 mt-2 font-semibold">Prova Final: 30min cronometrados · scorecard 4 dimensões · aprovação para ir ao ar</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-red-600 text-xl">→</div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 bg-black text-white rounded-xl p-6">
    <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">🟣 Critério de aprovação para a live</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-3">Você só vai ao ar se passar na <strong>Prova Final do Pilar 4</strong>. Scorecard ≥4/5 em todas as dimensões.</p>
    <p class="text-xs text-purple-400">Não é castigo. É garantia de que você entrou no ar com método — não com sorte.</p>
  </div>

  <footer class="text-center text-xs text-gray-400 py-8 mt-8">
    Curso gerado pelo Orquestrador OnLive v4 · {{brand.name}} · {{live.date}}
  </footer>
</main>

</body>
</html>
